<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>cryptoCat</title>
    <style>
        /* Resetting margin and padding for consistency */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa, #c3cfe2);
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .info {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 400px;
        }

        .info h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }

        .info p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        form {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 400px;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }

        button:focus {
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(72, 128, 74, 0.4);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .info, form {
                width: 100%;
                margin: 0 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="info">
        <h1>Welcome to CryptoNode</h1>
        <p>This is a private, encrypted chat service.</p>
        <p>Click the button below to generate a private chat link. The link will appear at the top of the chat. Share it with the second person to start a secure conversation.</p>
    </div>
    <form action="/" method="POST">
        <button type="submit">Generate p2p Chat</button>
    </form>
</body>
</html>
